{{Orphan|date=January 2013}}

The '''M&T Bank Pavilion''' is located on Eutaw Street in downtown [[Baltimore, Maryland]]. Originally this building housed a [[bank]]. The building was renovated and reopened in 2004 as part of the [[France-Merrick Performing Arts Center]], and currently serves as a banquet hall and multi-use space.

The M&T Bank Pavilion is adjacent to the [[Hippodrome Theatre, Baltimore|Hippodrome Theatre]].

