'''''Planning Magazine''''' is a monthly publication of the [[American Planning Association]].<ref>{{cite news|author=Chris Steins|title=Do You Read These Planning Magazines?|url=http://www.planetizen.com/magazines|accessdate=January 10, 2017|work=Planetizen|date=June 29, 2010}}</ref> The headquarters is in [[Chicago]]. It offers news and analyses of events in planning (including suburban, rural, and small [[Urban planning|town planning]], [[environmental planning]], neighborhood revitalization, [[economic development]], [[Social engineering (political science)|social planning]], and [[urban design]]).
