{{Infobox person | name = Safet Gjici | image = | caption = | birth_name = Safet Gjici | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1972|4|30|mf=y}} | birth_place = [[Kukës]], [[Albania]] | residence = | religion = | nationality = Albanian | party = [[Socialist Party of Albania|Socialist Party]] | alma_mater = [[University of Tirana]] | employer = | salary = | occupation = President, [[FK Kukësi]] | spouse = | children = 4 | boards = | net_worth = }}
'''Safet Gjici''' (born 30 April 1972 in [[Kukës]]) is an [[Albania]]n businessman who is the CEO of EuroGjici Security and Kevin Construction. He is also the president of [[Albanian Superliga]] football club [[FK Kukësi]]. He was the [[Socialist Party of Albania|Socialist Party]] candidate in the [[Kamëz|municipality of Kamëz]] in the [[Albanian local elections, 2015|2015 local elections]], but he lost to the [[Democratic Party (Albania)|Democratic Party]] candidate Xhelal Mziu.<ref>[http://www.panorama.com.al/bashkia-kamez-mziu-ne-kerkim-te-mandatit-te-trete-perballe-gjicit-qe-la-postin-e-prefektit/ Bashkia Kamëz]</ref><ref>[http://www.gazetatema.net/web/2014/03/27/shkarkohet-besnik-dervish-safet-gjici-prefekti-i-kukesit/ Prefekt i Kukësit]</ref>
